## Financial Results & Analysis

### Revenue Profile Evolution

**Phase 1: High-Revenue Period (2025-2034) - Full Incentive Coverage**
- **Annual Revenues:** €2.85M - €3.35M
- **Revenue Mix:** 
  - 52% from FIT (Plant A)
  - 38% from PPAs (Plants B & C)
  - 10% merchant market
- **Stability:** High (85%+ contracted revenues)

**Phase 2: Moderate Revenue (2035-2044) - Partial Incentive**
- **Annual Revenues:** €2.45M - €2.05M
- **Revenue Mix:**
  - 73% from FIT (Plant A only)
  - 27% merchant market (Plants B & C fully merchant)
- **Stability:** Medium (73% contracted, but merchant exposure rising)

**Phase 3: Full Merchant Exposure (2045-2049) - No Incentives**
- **Annual Revenues:** €1.58M - €1.63M
- **Revenue Mix:** 100% merchant market (all plants)
- **Stability:** Low (full merchant risk)

**Critical Observation:** **43% revenue cliff** from Year 20 (2044: €2.05M) to Year 21 (2045: €1.58M) when FIT expires. This creates tail-end cash flow risk for equity investors.

### Operating Performance Metrics

**EBITDA Margins:**
- **Early Years (2025-2030):** 81-82% (high-margin due to FIT/PPA floors)
- **Mid-Life (2031-2044):** 76-78% (stable operational efficiency)
- **Late Life (2045-2049):** 70-72% (margin compression from lower merchant prices)

**Cash Flow Generation:**

| Period | EBITDA | NOPAT | OFCF | Cumulative OFCF |
|--------|--------|-------|------|-----------------|
| **Years 1-5** | €12.3M | €9.1M | €10.0M | €10.0M |
| **Years 6-10** | €12.1M | €8.9M | €9.9M | €19.9M |
| **Years 11-15** | €11.5M | €8.5M | €9.4M | €29.3M |
| **Years 16-20** | €10.1M | €7.4M | €8.4M | €37.7M |
| **Years 21-25** | €7.8M | €5.8M | €6.8M | €44.5M |
| **TOTAL (25Y)** | **€53.8M** | **€39.7M** | **€44.5M** | - |

**Free Cash Flow After Debt Service:**
```
Total OFCF (25 years): €44.5M
Total Debt Service (15 years): €36.7M
Net Cash to Equity: €7.8M
```

### Debt Analysis & Coverage Ratios

**DSCR Performance:**

| Period | Min DSCR | Max DSCR | Avg DSCR | Lender Covenant | Status |
|--------|----------|----------|----------|----------------|--------|
| **Years 1-5** | 1.91x | 2.06x | 1.98x | > 1.20x | ✅ Pass |
| **Years 6-10** | 1.97x | 2.18x | 2.08x | > 1.20x | ✅ Pass |
| **Years 11-15** | 1.84x | 2.68x | 2.17x | > 1.20x | ✅ Pass |
| **Post-Debt (16+)** | N/A | N/A | N/A | Debt paid off | - |

**Minimum DSCR: 1.84x (Year 11)**  
**Maximum DSCR: 2.68x (Year 15)**  
**Average DSCR: 2.08x (Years 1-15)**

**Credit Assessment:** Portfolio maintains **robust** debt serviceability with 70%+ cushion above minimum 1.20x covenant. Lowest coverage occurs in Year 11 due to Plant C transitioning to lower merchant prices post-PPA expiry.

**Debt Amortization Schedule:**

```
Year  | BOP Debt  | Principal | Interest | Total DS  | EOP Debt  | DSCR
------|-----------|-----------|----------|-----------|-----------|------
2025  | €21.0M    | €1.4M     | €1.05M   | €2.45M    | €19.6M    | 1.91x
2030  | €14.0M    | €1.4M     | €0.70M   | €2.10M    | €12.6M    | 2.08x
2035  | €7.0M     | €1.4M     | €0.35M   | €1.75M    | €5.6M     | 2.35x
2039  | €1.4M     | €1.4M     | €0.07M   | €1.47M    | €0.0M     | 2.68x
2040+ | €0        | -         | -        | -         | -         | N/A
```

### Return Analysis

**Equity IRR Calculation:**
```
Initial Equity Investment: -€6.0M (Year 0)
+ Net Cash to Equity (Y1-Y25): +€7.8M
+ Residual Asset Value (Y25): €0 (conservative - panels at end of life)

IRR to Equity: 9.8% (post-tax, post-debt)
```

**Interpretation:** 9.8% IRR exceeds typical infrastructure fund hurdles (7-8%) and compensates for renewable energy risks (regulatory, merchant price, technology degradation).

