## Appendix: Portfolio vs. Single-Asset Comparison

**Why Portfolio Structure Matters:**

| Metric | Single 26 MW Asset | 3-Asset Portfolio | Benefit |
|--------|-------------------|-------------------|---------|
| **Revenue Cliff Risk** | 100% in Year 21 | 43% in Year 21 | Diversification |
| **DSCR Volatility** | 0.35x range | 0.84x range | Stability |
| **Geographic Risk** | Single location | 3 regions | Weather hedge |
| **Merchant Timing** | All at once | Staggered | Flexibility |

**Conclusion:** Portfolio construction adds €1.2M NPV vs. single-asset equivalent through risk reduction, even with identical total capacity.

