## Financial Model Snapshot

**Key Formulas Reference:**
```excel
// Revenues by stream
FIT_Revenues = Production_A × FLAG_FIT × €70/MWh
PPA_Revenues_B = Production_B × 25% × FLAG_PPA_B × €55/MWh
PPA_Revenues_C = Production_C × FLAG_PPA_C × €65/MWh
Merchant_Rev = (Prod_A × FLAG_Mkt_A + Prod_B × (25%+75%×FLAG) + Prod_C × FLAG_Mkt_C) × Price_Inflated

// Operating Free Cash Flow
OFCF = (EBITDA - Taxes) + Depreciation - CapEx - ΔWorking Capital
Where: Taxes = EBIT × 24%, CapEx = 0 (operational asset), ΔWC = 0 (stable operations)

// Debt Service Coverage Ratio
DSCR = OFCF / (Principal_Payment + Interest_Payment)
Covenant Trigger: DSCR < 1.20 → Cash Sweep to Lenders
```
